content: Motivating
Using this with tabex, 2 months in, all good
This is such a great app. It has really helped me with my journey to quit smoking. I wish this was around 16 years ago.
Honestly, the best app I've found so far to help with trying to quit/ successfully quitting.

I love this app so much that I bought the pro version. It is making quitting smoking so much easier. I highly recommend it. I love the diary function and the motivation reminders. There are lots of achievements that keep you going. I have used other apps before but this one is different. It helps me get through cravings and tracks what triggers them. It has a slow quit function for those who want to quit gradually. Lots of helpful hints. Definitely Recommend.
Not a good app. The timer between cigarettes is not accurate, don't get this app

Just downloaded the app yesterday. Really like having the option for slowly quitting and how it counts down to quit day. Great detailed info on money saved, health and craving triggers. Will hopefully update with some good news in the New Year. Great app overall. Worth buying the Pro Version.

Good app, purchased Pro. 1. Colours - Start with a better app theme. 2. Motivations - Please use a default list or link to website for importing list. 3. Diary - allows export to drive/txt file. 4 Games - add a few more!!
Excellent Love it!

Ive been using this app when I try and quit for a couple of years now and even paid for it. It is cool. It has a lot of features! I am quitting again so my wife will think I am more attractive, for my health and for my children so they dont remember their daddy as a stinky smoker. I am excited to breathe easier, smell nice and start swimming, running, jumping rope, playing basketball and having relations again without my body being under the influence of a highly addictive vascular constrictor.
Loving it so far. I hope that I can quit long term.

7 days into quitting, this really helps me keep on track of all the positives of quitting, it's beey easy to fall into negative thoughts, I've been a smoker since i was 13, im now 32. I wanna see what 19 years without smoking looks like. Brilliant app, maybe add a few more puzzle games to help beat the craving, crosswords, wordfinds, maths quiz, anything to get the mind active :) Other than that, thankyou very much!
I keep trying until I succeeded, all this time EasyQuit was there for me!
Can't wait to start! Or QUIT!!
Helpful
Very interactive and helpful app. Needs a setting where you add if your on nictotine replacement therapy
Excellent!
Great app that's really helped me quit. The goals, along with notifications of achievements and personal motivations for quitting are excellent.

For me, this app works better than most. It let's me set my own schedule for quitting. The ones I've tried say they do, but this app feels different. It's not boxy or rigid like the other ones I've tried with high reviews. This app also has the same motivations and stats the other app do.
Really good information and keeps you on track
Great app to keep you on track!
Really helps me and encourages me to continue!

Update: After 8.5 months, I'm still going strong, because this app is there for me every step of the way. Worth paying the small price of the paid version. Previous review: Yesterday is five weeks, cold turkey. Couldn't have done it without the support from this app. Best investment I've ever made. Thank you! PS: the application developer responded very quickly to my support request for more information about a feature. Most appreciated.
I started my quit journey today. Enjoy this app

Smoker for nearly ten years. This app worked for me and I've been smoke free since May of 2019. The app made me realize how I really couldn't afford to just have a cigarette every once in a while, without completely restarting my body's recovery.
I think the app needs to be personalized more. Options to move button locations. A time graft of how often I smoke, how many i smoke per day with that section as well.
I'm only a couple of days into quitting. I chose the quit slowly option. It's very clear and seemingly easy steps. There are many useful parts to this app. Well worth the money.

I have found this app very very helpful at keeping me grounded through the quitting process. It's nice to have a "beat the craving" option, the reminders are really helpful and seeing the money add up is wonderful. The app wont make you quit, nothing can do that. But if you are committed to quitting, this app will definitely help!
Awesome app. Love how it tracks and gives stats.
Best ever!
Love the app. It helps alot to watch your progress and the money you are saving. Also pay the beat an urge game all the time!! Thanks
Great help to quit smoking. Love the health benefits.
21 days thanks to this app!
I love this app.
Helpful
Amazing, but doesn't give me any type of milestone notifications like the alcohol app does.

This app helps me see all the positive changes happening in my life. It shows money saved, but more important to me, time that has been added back to my life! I have smoked for 31 years... finally I found a tool I can use so easily and quickly to help me in those tough minutes! Love the Beat the Creaving game too!!
Doesn't save the pictures for you treats
Very helpful
Thanks for have done this app when i feel in abstinence i open it and i feel better
Been a couple weeks now and I love the part Where you can pace yourself to quit smoking and not just cold turkey
Super helpful!!!
This is a great app that has really helped me stop smoking and that continues to help me stay stopped.
Good
Very Informative. I love it. 🤗
Good app and smoke free, stay away from the devil 😁
of course it doesn't make you quite, but is good help, useful info and motivation.
good app
i love this app because in my mind when i want a cigarette i look to see how many cigarettes i have not had. with this app and my tablets i got off the doctors i think i might have cracked it.
Only thing that keeps me on track and motivated.
this is fantastic so glad I found it. It's making the whole experience so much easier.

Been using this app for sometime at several attempts to stop smoking. This time been able to stay off for 80 days and hopefully I don't relapse. This app has been really helpful to keep me off and I highly recommend as a tool to help you quit.
the badges really motivated me and i've been smoke free for over a year now after smoking 25 cigarettes per day for over 20 years
Great app
so far so good. contains really useful features for reducing cravings
A really good motivation tool. On day 17 and feeling good about myself!

Really helpful. thanks for putting so much effort into helping people stop smoking. update. Its now been a officially the longest time i have not smoked. im actually going to upgrade this app. Not cuz i need to but because it helped change my life. Thank you very much
Best app. Ive found to quit smoking
I am getting used to the app I kinda wish it had a little of instructions or a tour of what little square is for
This app has helped me stop smoking.
Just started slow quit. Good so far!
it helps
ģreat app, been smoke free now for a week. the app keeps me going
Works great. The purchase version offers a lot of motivational insights to stay the course.
great app. I'm 33 days smoke free. I really enjoy seeing my progress.
very helpful
Easy to use, great app and very helpful.
helps being able to set goals and see your progress.
Love this app.
Simple and very helpful.
intuitive, really encouraging! one week down!
very cool app. i like it. full version because of an awesome developer
I like this app. I just stop smoking so my mood is a little off beat but happy to have found this app. Every little bit helps!!!
It's a good app. No problems with it.
Great app. Helps a lot. Quiting was easier thanks to this app
The game part in it... To try and make it through the urge. I can only match one thing and nothing else ? Idk if I'm missing something or its a bug..

Works great
Great app. Major help.
Super helpful. Nice to see how much money I have saved.
Love it, 6 days smoke-free. Bought the pro-version to support the developer and to get rid of the ads.
Day 2, so far so good.

Best app for quitting smoking.
This app has greatly helped me achieve my goal, it is exactly what I needed! Perfect app!

I have brought the application but found no extra feature except no advertisment .To my utter surprise the application does not have the edit facility about when I quit if u type wrong date accidentally .It's a disaster if paid for it but good if u used it for free that means it unpaid application .I thought of giving one star only

3 days smoke-free, this app has made it a lot easier to keep me motivated. It has auto reminders that pop up (your personal reasons for quitting) and keeps a running total of how many cigarettes you would have smoked, how much money you've  saved so far and all of the real-time health benefits of quitting down to the hour (i.e. lung health 20% healed by day 4 smoke-free, etc.) I highly recommend this app!
Keeps me motovated...
Enjoy how positive this app is. Quitting is hard. This app makes me more motivated to go for it.
Good work.
The random messages to myself and the money tracker both worked well for me. Easy to set up and use.
Great App, would request the Dev forward a dark gray/black gradient background option in an update. Thank you in advance.
Helps me a lot...
Good app too expensive though...
Nice supportive app helps quitting with the fags. Thanks!
It work very well.
Great app

Easy to use and understand with a wide variety of motivational tools. I'm 3 days along and still smoke free (early I know) this app has played a big part in keeping me on the path to being completely smoke free.
Good app, really helps
This is helpful

I like the design and the memory game
God that it has a cheating option. Not available in onther apps.

I like the app but there are a few things I am having issues with.  First, I am quitting slowly but it still takes today's date as my quit day which is not true.   Second, it is not giving me an option to say how many smokes I have had today  Third, I am getting badges for being smoke free because I can't enter if I have a smoke or not so the badges are not real.   Please help me figure these things out and I will give a full rating. Those are my only issues. Thank you.
Love this app. Helps track  cigarettes not smoked and cash saved.

It's pretty, and it's functional.  I like the health things.  The random motivational notifications don't work. Well, when you go into the edit screen, Then you get a notification. I guess I'm not surprised; I was surprised there weren't any settings for, say, frequency or number of notifications. Too bad, I put my best work there.

Great way to keep up with my progress. I'm into my 3rd day of not smoking and this app has been my go to for support and encouragement, more than anything! I love being able to see how much time I've added to my life by not smoking!

This app is so helpful! I love the random reminders where you can list all the different reasons to stop smoking and it cycles through to remind you. I also like that it has a feature for allowing you to beat a craving.
Very good app..... I'm just starting  out and finding it useful
I use it with a book. Together they work.  I like the health stats on the app.
Just started today! It is easy to use.
So far so good. Like the health information in particular.  Will update.
I'm actually staying on track with this! I've teamed it with the pedometer and the fitness app, and love that I can track my progress in all areas.
Still working great as a motivational tool to stay smoke free.
Helpful application but need more enhancements
Great

great

Love it!

This app is so helpful. It's been very well thought out and offers supportive advice and a wealth of info crucial to aid your motivation to quit. I've tried quite a few quit-apps and this is my favourite. 🚭
Love it!
Day one of quiting and everything about this app helps,
The memory games to wait out an urge to smoke is a good addition. Love the app
Love the look and functions of this app. Really enjoy the match game as a distraction and the ability to store my own motivation.
